        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Sometimes Qu stays silent, as if silently approving. Other times, she offers soft guidance. You quickly get a feel for the logic and priorities, and the work begins to flow more smoothly.'}"
